### Codex CLI Request with Reasoning - Responses API
### Expected: JSON response with reasoning and completion
### Responses API transforms input to chat completions format

POST {{host}}/v1/responses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-5.3-codex",
  "input": "Write a function that calculates fibonacci numbers",
  "stream": false,
  "reasoning": {
    "effort": "medium"
  }
}

### Responses API with Tools
### Expected: Tool result in response

POST {{host}}/v1/responses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "input": "What is 15 * 23? Use the calculator tool.",
  "stream": false,
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "name": "calculator",
      "description": "A simple calculator for math expressions",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "expression": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Mathematical expression to evaluate"
          }
        },
        "required": ["expression"]
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Responses API Streaming with Reasoning
### Expected: SSE stream with reasoning and completion

POST {{host}}/v1/responses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-5.3-codex",
  "input": "Explain why the sky is blue",
  "stream": true,
  "reasoning": {
    "effort": "low"
  }
}

### Responses API - Input as Array of Messages
### Expected: JSON response with completion

POST {{host}}/v1/responses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "input": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful assistant."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is 2 + 2?"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false
}
